task.summary: minor update to grunt file and header
Add a trailing slash, if the path is specified and doesn't contain one.
allow module binding to use containerless syntax
ensure that template is cleared, if module is cleared
protect against null being passed into module binding
ensure that data is cleared before requesting new module, so data can't bind against an incorrect template
ensure that ko.virtualElements is available to support KO 2.0.
fix IE < 9 issue with applying undefined as args. fixes #4
allow afterRender function to be different per module fixes #7
better detection of anonymous templates + bower file
Add the ability to call a dispose function when module is removed. Bump version to 0.5.0.
avoid dependencies on disposal check, even in dom disposal
add tests for configurable text plugin name
wrap afterRender callback, so it is not called until template is ready
update references to KO 3.0. update specs to be compatible.
allow afterRender on module binding to be defined later when passing an observable and initial value is null/undefined. fixes #16
integrate templateProperty changes with existing style
update to KO 3.1. update examples and optimized example.
ensure that valueAccessor is called later, so in KO 3.0+ dependencies in binding strings can be captured
0.7.2 - allow passing an afterRender function name as a string to be called off of the module
